Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:02.064 --> 00:00:03.980
KATHERINE KUAN: Hi, my
name is Katherine Kuan,

00:00:03.980 --> 00:00:05.890
and I'm a developer
advocate at Google.

00:00:05.890 --> 00:00:08.290
Today is Take Your
Parents to Work Day.

00:00:08.290 --> 00:00:10.150
Parents are going to
come in for a session,

00:00:10.150 --> 00:00:12.730
and we're going to teach them
the first steps in building

00:00:12.730 --> 00:00:13.910
an Android app.

00:00:13.910 --> 00:00:16.424
We're going to be using a
simple tool called the Android

00:00:16.424 --> 00:00:18.090
Visualizer, and we're
going to show them

00:00:18.090 --> 00:00:22.210
how they can write XML and
have it appear on a phone.

00:00:22.210 --> 00:00:24.580
We hope that they can
continue by taking

00:00:24.580 --> 00:00:28.060
our course on Udacity, which is
called Android for Beginners,

00:00:28.060 --> 00:00:31.500
and it's aimed at people with
no programming experience.

