I'm Marilyn Walter,

00:00:42.210 --> 00:00:44.059
and I'm a registered
nurse by profession.

00:00:44.059 --> 00:00:45.350
BRENT WALTER: I'm Brent Walter.

00:00:45.350 --> 00:00:47.040
