me, she gets a reminder

00:01:53.650 --> 00:01:55.352
on her phone to call Dad.

00:01:55.352 --> 00:01:57.810
MARILYN WALTER: We have a son
who just went off to college,

00:01:57.810 --> 00:01:59.430
