it to light for me.

00:02:10.270 --> 00:02:13.820
It was just so nice to know what
everyone's talking about when

00:02:13.820 --> 00:02:15.070
they talk about making an app.

00:02:15.070 --> 00:02:17.060
For someone like me, who's
pretty much a novice at it,

00:02:17.060 --> 00:02:18.143
it was a great experience.

00:02:18.143 --> 00:02:19.268
I really enjoyed the class.

00:02:19.268 --> 00:02:20.851
BRENT WALTER: What
